Title: Cotton-blend jacquard skinny pants

'T by Alexander Wang''s pants prove you can nail the logo trend even in pared-back basics. These cotton-blend pants have a flattering extra-high waist and hug you close for a skinny fit. The brand''s name is printed across its stretch waistband.
